{"tid":1533613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知下一步應該點做嘅人 我想問你地幾個問題","createTime":"2019-09-02T18:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:49:38.000Z","uid":313,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e4321ae573e89b84f66e36bd12bd032d4d4f0d39","tid":1533613,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"自問唔係一個聰明人<br />\n亦唔想被人話帶風向<br />\n所以我淨係問幾個問題<br />\n唔洗答我 喺心入面答自己就得<br />\n答完你要做乜係你嘅事<br />\n<br />\n對於一個國際都市嚟講<br />\n市區幾條街定係機場重要啲?<br />\n一個地區警署定係機場重要啲?<br />\n政總定係機場重要啲?<br />\n想將運動帶到國際層面 應該去邊?<br />\n去警署? 出市區行下街? 定係塞機場?<br />\n<br />\n點解每次話入機場都會有人出嚟spin?<br />\n點解機場post推極都沉?<br />\n點解政府開記招對機場隻字不提?<br />\n大家共識 邊個地方先係春袋?<br />\n<br />\n黑警死全家?<br />\n落力嗌多幾句啲黑警就會死 啱唔啱?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復</span>香港 時代<span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span><br />\n紅字對你嚟講係咩意義?<br />\n大家行下企下 叫下口號 就會實現?<br />\n<br />\n如果你係咁諗<br />\n麻煩你唔好嗌呢句口號<br />\n你係侮辱緊句口號<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港 九月 每個星期六日 全世界入機場 係咁多</strong>"},{"pid":"801f502bba7b624b760238dec31502378aa3913f","tid":1533613,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:23:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ebe326a1a6ddb98f669a71dce27de2675560446","tid":1533613,"uid":98926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:27:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8/9去美國領事館請願</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">派人道支援/過人權法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3i9E9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3i9E9a.png&h=b678595e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M80cCFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM80cCFS.png&h=5da9f118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有大量文宣推<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人權法</strong></span><br />\n