 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82c7ead9ae0146035a6d7133c885d46774a7460","tid":1533613,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:41:27.000Z","msg":"完全正確"},{"pid":"7b7d379b7f8c52e157c46db7d7d09f4854a5c4ed","tid":1533613,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d52be62528141c7528e2082d43aeac11882c0b7","tid":1533613,"uid":39502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:45:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得美領同機場一樣值得做"},{"pid":"ff0003e66bf5837be6a96d104e1b250984a85e89","tid":1533613,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=ab718a5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係有個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612 <br />\nTG: UuuncleK<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b075ce295a362697466473f5f16f67192af452b6","tid":1533613,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:41:48.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646975bf8e3d076b030c0408a784ce49ce87a4a5","tid":1533613,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0735a34f4a8ca756d0ff6faf2a4c05b7d8b87a2a","tid":1533613,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:33:19.000Z","msg":"12"},{"pid":"1c2006eabb2bfa5c6cfbbc86a585de943b0578e6","tid":1533613,"uid":313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d52be62528141c7528e2082d43aeac11882c0b7","tid":1533613,"uid":39502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:45:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得美領同機場一樣值得做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:35:25.000Z","msg":"同意 8/9去美領 其餘日子全部入機場"},{"pid":"68f119ccef90f190699bcfe0a97acc8bd069fa55","tid":1533613,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"#14"},{"pid":"cd41d906d9d365974ebc90f3bea053f4cba54cb1","tid":1533613,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d6409a7da6d351901da79b4eb2fec20179642e71","tid":1533613,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"#16"},{"pid":"a6eae6bd131c6ec5b8b6c2a3a83c5cde11d1